86
00:06:20,611 --> 00:06:21,853
If you want to be successful,

87
00:06:23,002 --> 00:06:25,034
you need to concentrate only
on your work.

88
00:06:26,479 --> 00:06:27,860
Do not get your hands on

89
00:06:28,431 --> 00:06:29,442
other people's work.

90
00:06:30,188 --> 00:06:30,980
Understand?

91
00:06:43,927 --> 00:06:44,813
I am sorry.

92
00:06:45,604 --> 00:06:47,489
I was arranging the meeting room

93
00:06:47,489 --> 00:06:49,727
