95
00:06:52,965 --> 00:06:53,793
Yes.

96
00:06:59,935 --> 00:07:01,823
This is very risky.

97
00:07:07,415 --> 00:07:08,602
If what I am doing

98
00:07:08,752 --> 00:07:09,803
can benefit our company,

99
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,063
it's worth trying.

100
00:07:13,162 --> 00:07:13,969
Let me help.

101
00:07:14,496 --> 00:07:15,169
It's all right.

102
00:07:29,512 --> 00:07:31,136
My brother gets angry too easily.

103
00:07:31,819 --> 00:07:33,268
I gave him some information,

104
00:07:33,417 --> 00:07:34,723
and he was so angry about it.

105
00:07:36,252 --> 00:07:39,165
