the past quarterly sales of our department.

108
00:07:45,897 --> 00:07:47,384
They are now having a meeting.

109
00:07:49,983 --> 00:07:52,258
He thought he was smart enough
to find our mistakes.

110
00:07:53,993 --> 00:07:55,623
Did you clean everything?

111
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:56,741
Yes, Boss.

112
00:07:57,087 --> 00:08:00,804
I guarantee there is no evidence left
that they can link to you.

113
00:08:03,663 --> 00:08:05,223
What is our next move?

114
00:08:58,932 --> 00:08:59,735
Hello, Mom?

115
00:09:00,412 --> 00:09:01,361
Are you still awake?

116
00:09:02,236 --> 00:09:03,024
My son...

117
00:09:03,024 --> 00:09:04,349
How can I go to bed?

118
00:09:04,557 --> 00:09:06,619
I couldn't contact you all day.

119
00:09:07,321 --> 00:09:08,584
