121
00:09:11,954 --> 00:09:12,978
I am sorry.

122
00:09:13,506 --> 00:09:15,078
I was very busy with work.

123
00:09:15,187 --> 00:09:16,177
So I turned off my mobile.

124
00:09:17,135 --> 00:09:18,014
